					p(style='font-size:12px;margin-bottom:0') PC Mag Editor’s Choice award image reprinted with permission. © 2012 Ziff Davis, Inc. All Rights Reserved.
					p(style='font-size:12px;') PC Mag quote reprinted from www.pcmag.com with permission. © 2012 Ziff Davis, Inc. All Rights Reserved.
					p(style='font-size:12px;') © London Trust Media, Inc. All Rights Reserved.
			.footer-column.footer-social
				p.footer-social__title Social
				+socialLinks
